msgid ""
"Aligns bottom of the inline object (e.g. image, table) to the bottom of the "
"text. Equivalent to [code]INLINE_ALIGNMENT_BOTTOM_TO | "
"INLINE_ALIGNMENT_TO_BOTTOM[/code]."
